'''''The Gravedigger's Wife''''' waa filim 2021 ah, oo uu agaasime ka yahay Khadar Ayderus Axmed.<ref name="aftab">Kaleem Aftab, [https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/407021/ "Review: The Gravedigger's Wife"]. ''Cineuropa''.</ref> Filimka ayaa ah mid ay iska kaashadeen shirkado ka kala socda Faransiiska, Soomaaliya, Jarmalka iyo Finland.<ref name="ScreenDaily">Lisa Nesselson, [https://www.screendaily.com/reviews/the-gravediggers-wife-cannes-review/5161184.article "‘The Gravedigger’s Wife’: Cannes Review"]. ''[[Screen Daily]].''</ref>

== Shirqool ==
Guuleed (Cumar Cabdi), oo ah qabuuraha xabaalaha Jabuuti, ayaa la daalaa dhacaya sidii uu u heli lahaa lacag uu ku bixiyo qaliinka marka xaaskiisa Nasra ([[Yasmiin Warsame]]) uu aad ugu bukoodo cudurka kalyaha.

== Bixinta iyo soo dhaweynta ==
Axmed filimkiisii ​​ugu horreeyay, filimku wuxuu dhiirrigeliyay geerida qoyskiisa ku dhawaad ​​toban sano ka hor.<ref name="balaga">Marta Balaga, [https://variety.com/2021/film/global/the-gravediggers-wife-khadar-ayderus-ahmed-1235065872/ "‘Finnish Cinema Is So White,’ Says ‘The Gravedigger’s Wife’ Helmer Khadar Ayderus Ahmed"]. ''[[Variety]].''</ref> Waxaa la toogtay 2019, in kasta oo sii deynta dib loo dhigay illaa 2021 sababta oo ah [[Korona fayras|masiibada KOVID-19]] iyo carqaladeyntii qeybinta filimka 2020.<ref name="balaga" />

Filimku wuxuu ka soo muuqday barnaamijka Toddobaadka Dhaleeceeyayaasha Caalamiga ah ee [[2021 Filimka Dabaaldag Cannes|Filimka Dabaaldag Cannes]] ee 2021.<ref name="aftab" /> Waxaa markii dambe la baaray [[Filimka Caalamiga ee Toronto Dabaaldag]] ee 2021, halkaas oo uu ka mid ahaa guuleystayaasha Abaalmarinta Codadka Amplify.<ref>Steve Pond, [https://www.thewrap.com/belfast-wins-toronto-film-festivals-peoples-choice-award/ "‘Belfast’ Wins Toronto Film Festival’s People’s Choice Award"]. ''[[TheWrap]].''</ref>  Waxaa loo xushay inay tahay soo gelitaanka Soomaaliga ee [[Abaalmarinta Akadeemiyada ee Filimka Muuqaalka Caalamiga ugu Fiican|Filimka Muuqaalka Caalamiga]] ee  [[Abaalmarinta Akadeemiyada 94aad]], markii ugu horreysay oo Soomaaliya ay soo gudbiso filim.<ref name="Somalia">[https://variety.com/2021/film/awards/international-feature-oscar-2021-submissions-1235066208/ 'The Gravedigger's Wife' Selected by Somalia's First Ever Oscar Committee]. ''Variety''.</ref>

''The Gravedigger's Wife'' ayaa 10kii<ref>[https://mobile.twitter.com/DailyJubba/status/1456546928662093848 Xaaska Xabaal Qodaha which is the ethnic name of the Gravedigger’s Wife, a critically acclaimed film and Somalia’s first ever Oscar submission for 2022 Academy Awards, will now be airing at the Somali National Theatre on 10th November 2021. Show up and see the theatrical release]. ee ''[[Twitter]]''. </ref> Nofeembar lagu daawaday magaalada Muqdisho ee [[Masraxa Qaranka Soomaaliya|masraxa qaranka]]<ref>[https://barwaaqotv.com/notice-national-theater-to-host-screening-prize-winning-film-the-gravediggers-wife-next-night/ Notice : National Theater To Host Screening Prize Winning Film, The Gravedigger’s Wife Next Night].</ref><ref>[https://mobile.twitter.com/KhadarM/status/1458581643766214661 The premiere of "The Gravedigger's Wife" in Mogadishu, Somalia last night at the National Theatre of Somalia. ❤️]. 2021-11-11.</ref>

